# id: AbstractXmlApplicationContext -> protected void loadBeanDefinitions(XmlBeanDefinitionReader reader) throws BeansException, IOException
commentText:
Load the bean definitions with the given XmlBeanDefinitionReader._

The lifecycle of the bean factory is handled by the {@link #refreshBeanFactory}_method_ hence this method is just supposed to load and/or register bean definitions._@param reader the XmlBeanDefinitionReader to use_@throws BeansException in case of bean registration errors_@throws IOException if the required XML document isn't found_@see #refreshBeanFactory_@see #getConfigLocations_@see #getResources_@see #getResourcePatternResolver
codeText: protected void loadBeanDefinitions(XmlBeanDefinitionReader reader) throws BeansException, IOException {_		Resource[] configResources = getConfigResources()__		if (configResources != null) {_			reader.loadBeanDefinitions(configResources)__		}_		String[] configLocations = getConfigLocations()__		if (configLocations != null) {_			reader.loadBeanDefinitions(configLocations)__		}_	}
